<section class="tsq-story shopify-section">
  <div class="tsq-story__inner">
    {%- if settings.logo != blank -%}
      <img src="{{ settings.logo | image_url: width: 120 }}" alt="{{ shop.name }}" class="tsq-story__logo">
    {%- endif -%}
    <span class="tsq-eyebrow">Our Heritage</span>
    <div class="tsq-divider"></div>
    <h2>Born in Australia.<br>Inspired by the East.</h2>

    <p class="tsq-story__body">The Scent Quarter began with an obsession. A group of fragrance lovers right here in Australia fell head over heels for the art of Arabian perfumery — the deep oud, the smoky resins, the lush florals and warm ambers that define Gulf culture. What started as a personal passion became a mission: to share these extraordinary scents with fellow Australians.</p>

    <p class="tsq-story__body">We source directly from the most respected houses in the Gulf — Lattafa, Afnan, Rasasi, Armaf, Gissah and more. Every fragrance is authentic, hand-inspected, and decanted with care. We believe you shouldn't have to commit to a full bottle to find your signature scent, which is why we've made world-class Arabian perfumery available from just $15.</p>

    <p class="tsq-story__body">This is not just retail. It's a passion project rooted in culture, craftsmanship, and community — built right here in Australia, for anyone who believes that extraordinary fragrance shouldn't cost a fortune.</p>

    <a href="/collections/all" style="font-family:var(--tsq-ui);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tsq-gold);border-bottom:1px solid var(--tsq-gold);padding-bottom:3px;display:inline-block;margin-top:28px;">
      Explore our collection →
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "TSQ Story",
  "tag": "div",
  "class": "shopify-section"
}
{% endschema %}
